Package: cohortTdd
Type: Package
Title: Test-Driven Development for OHDSI Cohort Definitions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bill", "Baumgartner", email = "william.baumgartner@cuanschutz.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for testing OHDSI cohort definitions using synthetic patient data. 
    Provides parameterized testing framework that automatically validates cohort logic 
    against expected patient inclusion/exclusion patterns using TestGenerator and CDMConnector.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bill-baumgartner/cohortTdd
BugReports: https://github.com/bill-baumgartner/cohortTdd/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    TestGenerator,
    CDMConnector,
    dplyr,
    readxl,
    checkmate,
    omopgenerics
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    devtools,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
